{"lemma":"عَبْلَيْ","slug":"عَبْلَيْ","root":"ع.ب.ل","root_slug":"ع-ب-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ب-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":8,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":13},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n27883","","n27885","n27886","n27887"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%92%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be bulky, to be thick, to be gross; to become bulky, to become thick, to be gross"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to abound with leaves"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"synonym of عَبُلَ (ʕabula)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"synonym of عَبُلَ (ʕabula)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cut off, to extirpate, to separate"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to repel, to hinder, to impede, to prevent"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to twist, to contort"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"synonym of عَبَلَ (ʕabala)"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"bulky, thick, gross"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of عَبَلَ (ʕabala) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of عَبِلَ (ʕabila) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"twisted leaves or sprigs; cilium"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"twisted leaves or sprigs; Calligonum gen. et spp."}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27883","headword_ar":"عَبُلَ","root":"Ebl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] (S, O, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EabaAlapN","text_ar":"عَبَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, large, big, bulky,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thick;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eabala","text_ar":"عَبَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EubuwlN","text_ar":"عُبُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TK;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eabila","text_ar":"عَبِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EabalN","text_ar":"عَبَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eabalahu","text_ar":"عَبَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Az, O, * K,) [aor., app.,"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in other senses of the trans. verb,] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EabolN","text_ar":"عَبْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Az, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cut it off,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, O, * K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as to extirpate it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"this is the primary signification [of the trans. verb]. (Az, TA.) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eabalatohu Eabuwlu","text_ar":"عَبَلَتْهُ عَبُولُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K, [but in the copies of the K erroneously written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EabuwlN","text_ar":"عَبُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) said of a man when he has died, (O,) means, (K,) or is like, (O,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEabatohu $aEuwbu","text_ar":"شَعَبَتْهُ شَعُوبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Death separated him"},{"kind":"text","text":"from his companions; or, accord. to the primary signification of the verb,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"death cut him off,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extirpated him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (O;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ai$otaEabatohu $aEuwbN","text_ar":"اِشْتَعَبَتْهُ شَعُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K. [But correctly as in the O.]) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eabala Al$~ajarapa","text_ar":"عَبَلَ الشَّجَرَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EabolN","text_ar":"عَبْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He removed the leaves from the tree;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eab~alahaA","text_ar":"عَبَّلَهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (CK: but not in my MS. copy of the K, nor in the TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eabalahu","text_ar":"عَبَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IAar, O, K,) aor. and inf. n. as above, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He repelled it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, O, K;) namely, a thing. (K.) [See also the pass. part. n., below.] ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, hindered, prevented, impeded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"withheld, him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"diverted him by occupying him otherwise."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA Eabalaka","text_ar":"مَا عَبَلَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What diverted thee by occupying thee otherwise?"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hindered thee,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.? (TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eabalotu AlHabola","text_ar":"عَبَلْتُ الحَبْلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EabolN","text_ar":"عَبْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I twisted the rope."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eabalotu","text_ar":"عَبَلْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~ahoma","text_ar":"السَّهْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ks, S, O, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ks, O, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EabolN","text_ar":"عَبْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I put,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made, to the arrow a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miEobalap","text_ar":"مِعْبَلَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Ks, S, O, K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eabalotuhu","text_ar":"عَبَلْتُهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I shot him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shot at him, with a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miEobalap","text_ar":"مِعْبَلَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eabala bihi","text_ar":"عَبَلَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went away with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took away, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.)       -A5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ebl Al$~ajaru","text_ar":"عبل الشَّجَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eabala","text_ar":"عَبَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but perhaps a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEobala","text_ar":"اَعْبَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The trees put forth their leaves:"},{"kind":"text","text":"on the authority of Az. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","K","Az","TA","IAar","Ks"]},{"entry_id":"n27885","headword_ar":"عَبْلٌ","root":"Ebl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Large, big, bulky,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thick;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EabilN","text_ar":"عَبِلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) fem. of the former with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": and pl. [masc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EibaAlN","text_ar":"عِبَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K, TA,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DixaAmN","text_ar":"ضِخَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of the syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaxomN","text_ar":"ضَخْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EabolapN","text_ar":"عَبْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EabolaAtN","text_ar":"عَبْلَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, TA,) [with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"b","text_ar":"ب"},{"kind":"text","text":"quiescent,] because it is an epithet. (TA.) It is applied in this sense to anything. (K.) Thus, in a trad., it is applied to a man. (TA.) And one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN Eabolu Al*~iraAEayoni","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ عَبْلُ الذِّرَاعَيْنِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man large,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the fore arms."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb. *) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"farasN EabolN Al$~awaY","text_ar":"فَرَسٌ عَبْلٌ الشَّوَى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A horse thick in the legs."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AimoraA^apN EabolapN","text_ar":"اِمْرَاَةٌ عَبْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A woman complete,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perfect, in make"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"formation."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AimoraA^apN EabiylapN","text_ar":"اِمْرَاَةٌ عَبِيلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A large, big, bulky,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, O,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thick, woman."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, O, K. *) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAbilN","text_ar":"عَابِلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a boy, or young man, signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [so] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EabuwlN","text_ar":"عَبُولٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a woman: pl. of both"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EubulN","text_ar":"عُبُلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","S","O","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n27886","headword_ar":"عَبَلٌ","root":"Ebl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hadabN","text_ar":"هَدَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. (S, O)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Any leaves that are"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as though they were"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twisted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not expanded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) [generally meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slender sprigs, like strings, garnished with minute, amplexicaul, appressed, acute leaves, overlying one another like the scales of a fish,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as those of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TarofaA='","text_ar":"طَرْفَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroTaY","text_ar":"اَرْطَى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^avol","text_ar":"اَثْل"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the like of these:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) and, (K,) as some say, (TA,) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fruit of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArTY","text_ar":"ارطى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA:) and, (K,) as some say, (TA,) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hadab","text_ar":"هَدَب"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thereof, when they have become thick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the hot season, and red,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and fit to be used for tanning therewith:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slender leaves:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like of leaves, but not"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what are commonly called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leaves:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as are falling thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) i. e., of leaves: (TA:) and [in the CK “ or ”]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as are coming forth"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) thus having two contr. significations. (K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n27887","headword_ar":"عَبِلٌ","root":"Ebl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EabolN","text_ar":"عَبْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", first sentence."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}